channel.title: Blank client
channel.description:
To help stop leechers i made it closed source u can always do something to make it open again... very easy. also i did this because it makes the client size smaller. right now its larger than normal because of SWAT's emote system.
Features: Swats new emote system Vengeance emote (i think its 4410) Moving water 317 gameframe and sideicons 377 cache includes new items like ids 6200-7500 Fixed pack 86 error
